{"tid":303024,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"余文樂難得曬女友照放閃　粉絲敲碗快結婚","createTime":"2017-06-29T23:53:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T04:58:59.000Z","uid":81228,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"656f79e2467f7e11ca921c80ca5423909601c01c","tid":303024,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-29T23:53:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/29/phpCf70uz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2FphpCf70uz.jpg&h=c1400b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n余文樂（左）去年底大方認愛女友王棠云（右）。（合成圖，翻攝自余文樂、王棠云Instagram）<br />\n<br />\n〔娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕港星余文樂出道多年，感情世界備受關注，雖然曾傳出不少緋聞，卻鮮少公開認愛，去年底余文樂鬆口認了和「皮帶千金」王棠云熱戀，但仍相當低調。今日余文樂難得在Instagram曬出女友照片放閃。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/29/php6P863B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2Fphp6P863B.png&h=8554e9d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n余文樂難得放閃，公開曬出女友照片。（翻攝自余文樂Instagram）<br />\n<br />\n余文樂今日在Instagramg曬出一張照片，寫著「Small girl &amp; Big car」，只見女友王棠云開著他的愛車，看起來霸氣十足，雖然沒有甜蜜的話語，但余文樂罕見公開曬恩愛，也引起網友猜測兩人是否好事將近，紛紛敲碗表示「快結婚吧」、「快當爸爸生個孩子」、「這麼甜蜜該不會要結婚了」。<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2017/06/29/php4P7Bli.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2017%2F06%2F29%2Fphp4P7Bli.png&h=80a57d1f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王棠云是皮帶大王千金。（翻攝自王棠云Instagram）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2116097\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2116097&d=Lef6mzCXcJ9AA5ymDh00qJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6ce69b30\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fent.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F2116097&h=d9769974\" target=\"_blank\">http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2116097</a>"},{"pid":"c4807ef48f7127e4f8b23d55614d9c09